{"tid":2459631,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"乜原來依定消委會連電動車都試埋?","createTime":"2021-03-24T09:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:48:46.000Z","uid":224075,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5af24b136f10ff36162c4a1933308e844201cdf8","tid":2459631,"uid":224075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"消委會｜Tesla Model3長續航版電池續航力最強 6款電動車最高分<br />\n<br />\n政府近年推廣電動車，本月更將公布「電動車普及化路線圖」，擬訂在港推動電動車普及藍圖。最新一期消委會《選擇》月刊，比較了34款車輛的表現，當中11款為電動車，續航距離最佳的是Tesla Model 3 Long Range，推算續航距離可達425公里。<br />\n<br />\n根據消委會的總評分，奧迪（Audi）的兩款電動車e-tron Sportback及e-tron；Tesla的兩款電動車Model 3 Long Range及Model 3 Standard Range Plus；Volkswagen ID.3，以及平治 Mercedes-BenzEQC 400的評分，均達到4.5分，表現相對較好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/162540394_968286623977737_3206428204894018778_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=825194&amp;_nc_ohc=fWzoDmdQzLwAX9a5UIE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=a04285d975547b42df502a05f0cc9653&amp;oe=607EC646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F162540394_968286623977737_3206428204894018778_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D825194%26_nc_ohc%3DfWzoDmdQzLwAX9a5UIE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3Da04285d975547b42df502a05f0cc9653%26oe%3D607EC646&h=fd9b1d03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11a771588396ca4c664115318a960051e6293a68","tid":2459631,"uid":392206,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"睇Catalogue咪當試左羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82e3369029df30cafbdeda5f239ad37344da018","tid":2459631,"uid":291750,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"之後自用"},{"pid":"a6d368bb621a6b2a40efe7bb2c4981b936cf5b91","tid":2459631,"uid":125017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"上星期唔係講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wo